00:17:11,360 --> 00:17:13,260
 Mi smo tada molili zaista

474
00:17:13,260 --> 00:17:17,820
 i bilo je jedno prekrasno iskustvo za mene.

475
00:17:17,820 --> 00:17:19,620
 I preko tog iskustva,

476
00:17:19,620 --> 00:17:20,940
 reko te molitve za nerođene,

477
00:17:20,940 --> 00:17:23,060
 gospodin je opet nekako

478
00:17:23,060 --> 00:17:26,020
 moje srce zagrijavao.

479
00:17:26,020 --> 00:17:29,580
 Vraćao me tu ljubavi

480
00:17:29,580 --> 00:17:32,040
 i tu želju nekako.

481
00:17:32,140 --> 00:17:33,060
 jačala je želja u meni

482
00:17:33,060 --> 00:17:34,880
 da bi možda ipak postala redovnica.

483
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:36,720
 Kako je vrijeme više odmicalo,

484
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:38,480
 sve sam manje mogla sebe zamisliti

485
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:39,840
 da se udam,

486
00:17:39,840 --> 00:17:40,780
 da imam obitelj.

487
00:17:40,780 --> 00:17:43,040
 Nekako kod je to postalo strano odjednom

488
00:17:43,040 --> 00:17:45,140
 i nisam znala kako to,

489
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:46,720
 šta to, šta se događa.

490
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:49,960
 Kako je se jedna strana smanjivala,

491
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:50,740
 druga je jačala.

492
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:52,720
 I vjerujem da je zaista

493
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:54,180
 i ova molitva za nerođene,

494
00:17:54,180 --> 00:17:56,680
 da je to bilo jedna veliki,

495
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:58,260
 jedna odskočna daska

496
00:17:58,260 --> 00:17:59,780
 za prihvaćanje mojeg poziva.

497
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:03,660
 Tada sam,

498
00:18:03,660 --> 00:18:07,220
 sad da vidim dok le sam došla,

499
00:18:07,220 --> 00:18:07,940
 ja sam malo obajbila,

500
00:18:07,940 --> 00:18:09,440
 sam i popisivala neke stvari.

501
00:18:14,320 --> 00:18:16,900
 I tako je išla ta moja borba

502
00:18:16,900 --> 00:18:20,180
 do negdje Božića 2013. godine.

503
00:18:20,180 --> 00:18:23,080
 Taj Božić sam stvarno doživljela

504
00:18:23,080 --> 00:18:24,180
 najžalostnijim.

505
00:18:24,180 --> 00:18:26,840
 Isus mi je tada nekako,

506
00:18:26,840 --> 00:18:27,480
 mali Isus,

507
00:18:27,480 --> 00:18:28,520
 doslovica je mali,

508
00:18:28,520 --> 00:18:30,500
 mi je dao osjetiti

509
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:32,120
 koliko je malo voljen,

510
00:18:32,120 --> 00:18:33,700
 koliko ljudi

511
00:18:33,700 --> 00:18:37,060
 ne zanimaju se za njega.

512
00:18:37,060 --> 00:18:38,540
 Ljudi se spremaju za Božić,

513
00:18:38,540 --> 00:18:39,800
 kupuju darove,

514
00:18:39,800 --> 00:18:40,960
 čiste kuću,

515
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:42,680
 spremaju razne delicije

516
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:43,500
 i to sam vidjela

517
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:44,660
 i u svojoj obitelji

518
00:18:44,660 --> 00:18:46,480
 i tada me to tako,

519
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:46,620
 evo,

520
00:18:46,620 --> 00:18:48,020
 ja sam cijeli Božići

521
00:18:48,020 --> 00:18:49,520
 i badnjak

522
00:18:49,520 --> 00:18:50,220
 i prvi dan

523
00:18:50,220 --> 00:18:51,860
 doslovica je preplakala,

524
00:18:51,860 --> 00:18:52,760
 nisam znala

525
00:18:52,760 --> 00:18:54,240
 šta je to,

526
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:55,940
 zašto me to toliko boli,

527
00:18:55,940 --> 00:18:56,640
 ali evo,

528
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:57,920
 to je tada već bilo nekako

529
00:18:57,920 --> 00:18:59,220
 gdje je mali Isus

530
00:18:59,220 --> 00:19:00,520
 doticao moje srce

531
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:02,180
 i opet me je prevlačio k sebi.

532
00:19:02,180 --> 00:19:05,640
 Tada,

533
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:07,300
 nakon nekoliko dana,

534
00:19:07,300 --> 00:19:08,080
 bio je osmi,

535
00:19:08,080 --> 00:19:09,900
 prvi 2014. godine,

536
00:19:09,900 --> 00:19:12,320
 sjedila sam,

537
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:13,800
 bila sam u svom stanu

538
00:19:13,800 --> 00:19:15,180
 i skidala sam kuglice zbora

539
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:16,780
 i zaista je gospodinje

540
00:19:16,780 --> 00:19:18,000
 zanimljiv,

541
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:19,240
 kad i u kojem vremenu

542
00:19:19,240 --> 00:19:19,840
 mi progovara.

543
00:19:19,840 --> 00:19:21,960
 I dok sam tako skidala kuglice

544
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:23,480
 i u jednom tonutku

545
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:24,560
 sam čula

546
00:19:24,560 --> 00:19:26,360
 kako mi gospodin progovara.

547
00:19:26,360 --> 00:19:28,760
 Možeš bježati koliko god hoćeš,

548
00:19:28,760 --> 00:19:30,120
 ali kad tad

549
00:19:30,120 --> 00:19:31,260
 ićeš u samostal?

550
00:19:31,260 --> 00:19:33,560
 Kad tad išliš biti častna sestra?

551
00:19:33,560 --> 00:19:35,360
 I tada,

552
00:19:35,360 --> 00:19:37,880
 hoću samo to spomenuti,

553
00:19:37,880 --> 00:19:39,540
 kad god sam ja mislila

554
00:19:39,540 --> 00:19:40,920
 da mi gospodin nešto govori,

555
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:42,760
 uvijek u mene je bila euforija,

556
00:19:42,760 --> 00:19:43,760
 uvijek nešto.

557
00:19:43,760 --> 00:19:46,460
 I moj duhovnik mi je uvijek govorio

558
00:19:46,460 --> 00:19:47,960
 čekaj, čekaj,

559
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:48,880
 polako, polako.

560
00:19:48,960 --> 00:19:50,700
 u tom trenutku,

561
00:19:50,700 --> 00:19:52,720
 kad je tada gospodin zaista progovorio

562
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:53,320
 u mom srcu,

563
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:54,520
 u mom srcu je vladala

564
00:19:54,520 --> 00:19:57,600
 potpuni mir.

565
00:19:58,680 --> 00:19:59,780
 samo sam rekla dobro

566
00:19:59,780 --> 00:20:01,440
 i sjela.

567
00:20:02,300 --> 00:20:02,980
 i to je bilo to.

568
00:20:02,980 --> 00:20:05,080
 Za mene je tada se prelomila

569
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:07,800
 ta odluka,

570
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:08,820
 da li iću u samostal,

571
00:20:08,820 --> 00:20:09,240
 da li ne.

572
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:10,900
 Ja tada još uvijek nisam znala gdje.

573
00:20:11,940 --> 00:20:13,540
 tada sam ošla kod zvuk duhovnika

574
00:20:13,540 --> 00:20:13,900
 i mi kažem,

575
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:15,700
 ja ipak znam

576
00:20:15,700 --> 00:20:17,320
 da gospodin me zavedem u samostal.

577
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:17,640
 Kaže on,

578
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:19,320
 Bogu hvala da si ti više skontala.

579
00:20:19,320 --> 00:20:21,400
 I kaže on,

580
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,140
 pa gdje ćeš?

581
00:20:22,140 --> 00:20:23,000
 Pa joj velim,

582
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:25,080
 svakako u Bosnu.

583
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,760
 za mene nije bilo pitanje

584
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:27,880
 da li ću ostati u Austriji

585
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:28,680
 ili ću ići u Bosnu

586
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:29,280
 ili u Hrvatsku.

587
00:20:29,280 --> 00:20:30,320
 Ja sam rekla samo

588
00:20:30,320 --> 00:20:31,300
 ja u Bosnu idem,

589
00:20:31,300 --> 00:20:32,880
 ja u Austriji ne mogu,

590
00:20:32,880 --> 00:20:34,260
 nije to to.

591
00:20:34,260 --> 00:20:37,520
 I tada sam njemu rekla

592
00:20:37,520 --> 00:20:38,440
 idem ja u Bosnu

593
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:39,420
 kod onih mojih sistara

594
00:20:39,420 --> 00:20:40,480
 koje sam zvala,

595
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:40,740
 jeli,

596
00:20:40,740 --> 00:20:41,900
 2012.

597
00:20:41,900 --> 00:20:43,460
 Ovo je 2014.

598
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:45,480
 Nakon da što god unipod dana,

599
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:46,600
 god unipod dana

600
00:20:46,600 --> 00:20:47,860
 sam je bježala od mog poziva.

601
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:50,120
 I ja tada nazovem

602
00:20:50,120 --> 00:20:50,760
 evo sestru,

603
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:51,600
 admiratu,

604
00:20:51,600 --> 00:20:52,440
 koja je bila tada

605
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:54,300
 naša provincijska glavarica

606
00:20:54,300 --> 00:20:55,680
 i predstavim se

607
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,240
 i ona kaže

608
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:58,440
 joj, pa ne mogu vjerovati,

609
00:20:58,440 --> 00:20:59,620
 mi smo se baš misli

610
00:20:59,620 --> 00:21:00,380
 šta je s tobom.

611
00:21:00,380 --> 00:21:01,840
 I sestre su sjetle

612
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:02,820
 na večer zajedno.

613
00:21:02,820 --> 00:21:04,620
 One su to meni poslije rekli,

614
00:21:04,620 --> 00:21:05,740
 ja sam to poslije shvatila.

615
00:21:05,740 --> 00:21:07,220
 Osmi prvi je bio

616
00:21:07,220 --> 00:21:08,080
 Štadlerov dan.

617
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:09,080
 Znači ja sam,

618
00:21:09,080 --> 00:21:10,320
 to je moj pristanak

619
00:21:10,320 --> 00:21:12,240
 da idem,

620
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:14,540
 da postanem redovnica

621
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:16,700
 je bilo na njegov spomen dan.

622
00:21:16,700 --> 00:21:18,080
 Znači svakog osmog mjesecu

623
00:21:18,080 --> 00:21:19,580
 sestre obelježavaju

624
00:21:19,580 --> 00:21:20,840
 posebno njegov dan

625
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:21,620
 i molim mu se.

626
00:21:22,660 --> 00:21:24,320
 I baš na taj dan,

627
00:21:24,320 --> 00:21:25,880
 a ja znači ne znajući,

628
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:27,280
 još uvijek nisam znala ništa

629
00:21:27,280 --> 00:21:27,840
 o njemu osim

630
00:21:27,840 --> 00:21:29,400
 nekih pojedinosti

631
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:30,320
 evakvo maleni.

632
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:34,540
 I ja sam vrlo brzo se spakirala.

633
00:21:34,540 --> 00:21:36,980
 Ja sam već 11. prvog bila u Sarajevu.

634
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:39,440
 Dolazim na kolodvor u četiri ujutro,

635
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:40,640
 ne znam ni jednu sestru,

636
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:41,860
 nikog živog, ne znam.

637
00:21:41,860 --> 00:21:45,880
 I bila sam dva tjedna kod sestara.

638
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:48,860
 Ta dva tjedna su bila do tada

639
00:21:48,860 --> 00:21:50,080
 najljepša u mom životu.

640
00:21:50,080 --> 00:21:53,160
 Sestre, znači nisam poznavala ni jednu,

641
00:21:53,780 --> 00:21:55,640
 ali kad sam među njima bila,

642
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:56,600
 to je zaista,

643
00:21:56,600 --> 00:21:58,080
 koda smo odrasli zajedno,

644
00:21:58,080 --> 00:21:59,220
 koda sam jedna od njih,

645
00:21:59,220 --> 00:22:01,720
 koda smo obitelj,

646
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,000
 ne znam kako to opisati.

647
00:22:03,780 --> 00:22:06,800
 I nakon dva tjedna vraćam se kuće u Beć.

648
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:09,760
 Moji roditelji, svi izvan sebe,

649
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:11,620
 kakva Bosna, kakav samostan,

650
00:22:11,620 --> 00:22:13,040
 ko ti ispro mozak.

651
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:15,580
 Ali što su oni bili više protiv,

652
00:22:15,580 --> 00:22:16,540
 ja sam bila više za.

653
00:22:16,540 --> 00:22:19,820
 I opet je uslijedila, naravno,

654
00:22:19,820 --> 00:22:22,600
 jedna borba, jedno bježanje.

655
00:22:22,600 --> 00:22:25,180
 Misliš, nemoguće da je tako savršeno.

656
00:22:25,180 --> 00:22:28,420
 Nemoguće, Bože, pa to je sigurno neka zamka zloga.

657
00:22:28,420 --> 00:22:30,540
 Kako to može biti da dođem negdje,

658
00:22:30,540 --> 00:22:32,560
 da se tako uklopim među te sestre?

659
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:35,660
 Nemoguće, to je nešto, neka zamka.

660
00:22:35,660 --> 00:22:40,520
 I nakon, evo, skoro daljnih devet mjeseci,

661
00:22:40,520 --> 00:22:43,300
 kažem, meni moj duhovnik,

662
00:22:43,300 --> 00:22:44,940
 okej, ne može ovako dalje,

663
00:22:44,940 --> 00:22:47,160
 to mora doći kraj tome,

664
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,340
 ajmo se mi moli za jedan znak.

665
00:22:48,340 --> 00:22:50,460
 Rekao, dobro, ajmo se moli za znak.

666
00:22:50,460 --> 00:22:52,300
 I ja tada, evo,

667
00:22:52,300 --> 00:22:54,000
 sa njim smo se molili,

668
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:55,760
 na večer, evo, dođe,

669
00:22:55,760 --> 00:22:58,340
 izvuče mi jedan citat,

670
00:22:58,340 --> 00:23:01,320
 i kaže tada, iz prve knjige letopisa,

671
00:23:01,320 --> 00:23:02,700
 kaže, tada reče,

672
00:23:02,700 --> 00:23:04,540
 David svojemu sinu Salomonu.

673
00:23:04,540 --> 00:23:06,980
 Pođi na posao odvažno i smijelo,

674
00:23:06,980 --> 00:23:08,740
 ne boj se i ne plaši se,

675
00:23:08,740 --> 00:23:10,880
 jer Bog, Gospod, Bog moj,

676
00:23:10,880 --> 00:23:11,660
 bit će s tobom.

677
00:23:11,660 --> 00:23:13,400
 On te neće ostaviti,

678
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:15,180
 dok se ne dovrše svi radovi

679
00:23:15,180 --> 00:23:16,920
 za službu u hramu Gospodnjem.

680
00:23:17,980 --> 00:23:21,160
 tada sam zaista u tom trenutku osjetila da je to to.

681
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:25,200
 I u roku od par dana spakirala svoje stvarčice

682
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,500
 i odšla u Sarajevo.

683
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:28,480
 Relativno brzo,

684
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:29,480
 nakon, nakon,

685
00:23:29,480 --> 00:23:30,820
 nakon mog dolaska,

686
00:23:30,820 --> 00:23:32,520
 znači, drugog dolaska u Sarajevo,

687
00:23:32,520 --> 00:23:35,200
 ja sam dola odlaku da želim pristupiti,

688
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:37,760
 ali, družbi se stara služak i malog Isusa.

689
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:40,560
 I tek tada, što bi se rekla,

690
00:23:40,560 --> 00:23:42,540
 evo, tada sam ja tek to osvatila,

691
00:23:42,540 --> 00:23:45,340
 kako me, evo,

692
00:23:45,340 --> 00:23:46,660
 otacu temelitelj doslovce

693
00:23:46,660 --> 00:23:49,340
 od početka do ulazka u samostan pratio,

694
00:23:49,340 --> 00:23:50,860
 taj moj prvi neki,

695
00:23:50,860 --> 00:23:52,700
 da, gospodino je bio 8.1.

696
00:23:52,700 --> 00:23:54,360
 jer na njegov spomen,

697
00:23:54,360 --> 00:23:57,060
 došla sam u Bosnu 11.1.

698
00:23:57,060 --> 00:24:00,940
 jer je on je 11.1.1882 stupio u Bosnu.

699
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:03,120
 I na kraju sam, evo,

700
00:24:03,120 --> 00:24:04,680
 ušla službeno u kandidaturu

701
00:24:04,680 --> 00:24:06,460
 moje naše družbe

702
00:24:06,460 --> 00:24:09,100
 na bezgrašno začeće Blažne djevice Marije,

703
00:24:09,200 --> 00:24:13,020
 8.12. na dan njegovog rađenja za nebo.

704
00:24:13,020 --> 00:24:18,180
 Zaista sam bila zatečena,

705
00:24:18,180 --> 00:24:20,600
 nisam mogla vjerovati kako,

706
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:24,600
 kako gospodin vodi nečiji poziv,

707
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:25,380
 nečiji život.

708
00:24:25,380 --> 00:24:27,440
 I kad me neko danas pita,

709
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:29,180
 kako znati koji red,

710
00:24:29,180 --> 00:24:30,720
 kako znati gdje otići,

711
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:33,840
 onda zaista, ja samo kažem,

712
00:24:33,840 --> 00:24:35,200
 čitajte živote svetaca,

713
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:36,360
 čitajte o njima,

714
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:37,980
 i tamo gdje te prevuče,

715
00:24:37,980 --> 00:24:39,160
 gdje se ti osjećaš,

716
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,860
 kod kuće, gdje nešto imaš,

717
00:24:40,860 --> 00:24:43,160
 što bi ti štije učiniti,

718
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:43,920
 tamo idi.

719
00:24:43,920 --> 00:24:46,580
 To će vjerovatno pokazati se ispravnim.

720
00:24:46,580 --> 00:24:48,580
 Tamo gdje se čovjek osjeća kod kuće,

721
00:24:48,580 --> 00:24:51,780
 to je ona prava stvar.

722
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:54,980
 I evo, konačno sam i položila

723
00:24:54,980 --> 00:24:57,700
 svoje prve zavijete 2018. godine.

724
00:24:57,800 --> 00:25:00,000
 srstva Jelana imala tada svoje vječne zavijete,

725
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:01,740
 a ja svoje prve zavijete.

726
00:25:01,740 --> 00:25:04,120
 2018. godine, o jubilarnoj godini,

727
00:25:04,120 --> 00:25:07,920
 sto te obljetnice preminuća našeg otemelitelja,

728
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:09,060
 to je strođenja za nebo.

729
00:25:10,360 --> 00:25:12,680
 I vjerujem da je ovo moje svjeročanstvo

730
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:14,400
 je samo jedno u nizu

731
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:16,220
 i da druge srstve mogu posljedočiti

732
00:25:16,220 --> 00:25:18,680
 o sličnim iskustvima

733
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:20,080
 sa našim otemeliteljem.

734
00:25:20,080 --> 00:25:23,900
 On je zaista jedna posebna sobrost,

735
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:25,840
 kao što ćulio se sri Jelene večeras.

736
00:25:25,840 --> 00:25:28,540
 Što više o njemu saznaješ,

737
00:25:28,540 --> 00:25:30,300
 više te zadivljuje njegova ljubav

738
00:25:30,300 --> 00:25:31,500
 i njegova hrabrost

739
00:25:31,500 --> 00:25:33,500
 i silno pouzdanje u Boga koje je on imao.

740
00:25:33,500 --> 00:25:36,460
 Imao je jedno junačko srce

741
00:25:36,460 --> 00:25:39,280
 koje je ljubilo majčinskom ljubavi svakoga.

742
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:41,580
 Od kako svojih siroča,

743
00:25:41,580 --> 00:25:42,620
 tako svečenika,

744
00:25:42,620 --> 00:25:44,760
 tako nas svoje duhovne čeri

745
00:25:44,760 --> 00:25:46,400
 i tako svakog čovjeka.

746
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:50,960
 I evo, na kraju bi samo želila vas

747
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:52,560
 evo, hrabriti, dragi mladi

748
00:25:52,560 --> 00:25:55,600
 koji možda tražite još uvijek svoj pozi,

749
00:25:55,600 --> 00:25:56,360
 svoj put,

750
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:59,520
 da se odvažite živjeti za Krista,

751
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:00,520
 da se ne bojite,

752
00:26:00,520 --> 00:26:03,720
 jer to je zaista najljepši život.

753
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:05,560
 Mi mislimo da ćemo izgubiti svašta nešto

754
00:26:05,560 --> 00:26:07,340
 ako se odvažimo živjeti za njega,

755
00:26:07,340 --> 00:26:10,480
 ali dobivamo neizmjerno puno više

756
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:12,120
 i savršenije.

757
00:26:12,120 --> 00:26:13,920
 Od kad sam mu samostavno

758
00:26:13,920 --> 00:26:14,880
 mi je ispunio,

759
00:26:14,880 --> 00:26:17,920
 ma ne ispunio moje želje,

760
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:21,600
 nego više nego ono što sam mogla sanjati,

761
00:26:21,600 --> 00:26:23,760
 više nego što sam ja mogla zamisliti.

762
00:26:23,760 --> 00:26:27,860
 I čvrsto se održite naše nebeske majke Marije,

763
00:26:27,860 --> 00:26:29,700
 njoj se utječite svakog dana,

764
00:26:29,700 --> 00:26:31,920
 njezinu bezgrošnom srcu se posvetite.

765
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:33,880
 To je nešto moje osobno iskustvo

766
00:26:33,880 --> 00:26:35,500
 i tada ćete vidjeti zaista

767
00:26:35,500 --> 00:26:38,680
 kako se u vama i oko vas mijenja sve nabolje.

768
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:41,860
 I koje što je rekao jednom svijet Ivan Pavo drugi,

769
00:26:41,860 --> 00:26:45,420
 rekao je kao učinite od svog života remeg dijelo.

770
00:26:45,420 --> 00:26:48,060
 Kao što je to učinio i naš otac temelitelj,

771
00:26:48,060 --> 00:26:48,740
 Josip Štadler,

772
00:26:48,740 --> 00:26:51,400
 i mnogi drugi Boži miljenici.

773
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:54,220
 To želim svima nama i vama.

774
00:26:54,220 --> 00:26:56,260
 Nek vas prati Božji blagoslov.

775
00:26:56,260 --> 00:26:57,780
 Hvala.

